nodes.text: The Oniantae Hills was a hilly region on the Forest Moon of Endor. The moon's Smuggler Outpost was located very close to this region.

In the 2003 massively multiplayer online role-playing game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided, the Oniantae Hills were one of many designated planetary regions. The game, developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, was shut down on December 15, 2011.
